BC Image Alias extension FEATURES

1) BC Image Alias extension Features

The bcimagealias extension provides the following features and supported apis

   - BCImageAlias eZ Publish extension PHP Class, Creates, Regenerates,
     Removes image alias image variation image files for eZ Publish
   -- See: classes/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP Scripts, Creates, Regenerates,
     Removes image alias image variation image files for eZ Publish
   -- See: bin/php/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP Cronjob parts, Creates,
     Removes image alias image variation image files for eZ Publish
   -- See: cronjobs/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP Module views, Creates, Regenerates,
     Removes image alias image variation image files for eZ Publish
   -- See: modules/bcimagealias/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP workflow event, Creates, Regenerates
     image alias image variation image files for eZ Publish
   -- See: eventtypes/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP kernel class override for eZ Publish
   -- See: kernel/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension PHP lib class override for eZ Publish
   -- See: lib/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension design override 'standard' for eZ Publish
   -- See: design/standard/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension design override templates for content structure and popup class menus for eZ Publish admin siteaccess
   -- See: design/standard/templates/

   - bcimagealias eZ Publish extension translations for 'untranslated', 'eng-GB' and 'eng-US' in eZ Publish
   -- See: translations/


2) BC Image Alias extension eZ Publish api feature usage

The bcimagealias extension makes use of the following eZ Publish features and supported apis

   - eZ Publish extension
   - eZ Publish extension classes
   - eZ Publish extension bin/php scripts
   - eZ Publish extension settings overrides
   - eZ Publish extension design overrides
   - eZ Publish extension design template overrides
   - eZ Publish extension module views
   - eZ Publish extension workflow event
   - eZ Publish extension cronjobs
   - eZ Publish extension kernel class overrides
   - eZ Publish extension lib class overrides
   - eZ Publish extension extension.xml
   - eZ Publish extension ezinfo.php
   - eZ Publish extension translations

